==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: wŏnt, wōnt
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /wɒnt/, /wəʊnt/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /wQnt/, /w@Unt/
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-əʊnt|-əʊnt]]

===Noun===
'''wont''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# One's [[habitual]] way of doing things.
#:''He awoke at the crack of dawn, as was his '''wont'''.''

